story.title: Chasing Mr. Wrong - Episode 4
story.storyDescription: When you're 35, recently single and looking for a good time, all you have to do is swipe right - right?
story.creator: web-uploader

author.bio: Lee Bross is a multi-published author of YA and Adult romance living in coastal Maine.

story.prePaywallNotification: Will swiping right keep Steph from finding love IRL? Keep reading CHASING MR. WRONG.
story.postPaywallNotification: What does Steph do after she leaves the restaurant? Keep reading CHASING MR. WRONG.
